### POST /briscola/encode - Ottieni i 31 float dell'osservazione
POST https://hello-python.casa-terraneo.workers.dev/briscola/encode
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Secret: test-secret-1234

{
  "hand": [
    {"suit": "bastoni", "rank": 1},
    {"suit": "coppe",   "rank": 7},
    {"suit": "spade",   "rank": 3}
  ],
  "table": null,
  "briscola": {"suit": "denari", "rank": 10},
  "deck_left": 30,
  "my_score": 0,
  "opp_score": 0
}

